{
  "stem": "6989.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only reason that Lena said she was going to give me up is because she felt I would have a better life with her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like she could give me papers, and crayons, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I have to say, broken-heartedly, because for me to leave Lena was-- I think that I was more traumatized then than even-- because I was younger.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was going with somebody that I really loved and knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did go back with her to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She thought that I would have a better life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That she could give me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said it to her, but I heard it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I went back with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We traveled you know, through Moscow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She named me Shura.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Shifra.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was very-- for me, it was very traumatic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I just, you know, cried and cried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so did Lena.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because then we started to correspond.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so that-- from that time on, I did stay with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She, you know, her husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know what year it was, whether it was totally after the war or what.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Russians allowed Polish Jews to go back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever wanted to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had signed up to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know we traveled for a full month in the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not just us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many, many Jews that were Polish citizens, which we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from that time on, we traveled together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Russia, we stopped off in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we stayed, probably, a couple of nights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, we were scared to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because even after the war, they still--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
